name: Dune Grass
description: Signed Original Fine Art Photography Print by Kelly Ash. Title: Dune Grass Size: 8" x 10" I love the way Dune Grass blows in the wind ... it always reminds me of the Spring. Dune Grass provides amazing support, and it is through this grass that holds the beach in place. The grass has very long roots that intertwine and network that holds the sand in place so it doesn't erode away into the ocean. How can you not like this plant? name: Vintage Nest with Grape Hyacinth & Stock
description:
Signed Original Fine Art Photography Print by Kelly Ash.

Title: Nest of Garden Blooms
Size: 8" x 10"

I found this empty nest in a shrub I was pruning last fall, and stowed it away for a rainy day ... well that day came last spring when my grape hyacinths were blooming and I happened to have some lovely pink stock in a vase on my kitchen counter. So with a little care, Voila! I have a romantic little nest of garden blooms!

name: Green Hydrangea
description: Signed Original Fine Art Photography Print by Kelly Ash. Title: Green Hydrangea Size: 8" x 10" I know they are technically called "lime green" hydrangeas, but I don't think there is anything lime about this plant! Hydrangeas are such a wonderful plant, since they provide beauty to your landscape in the spring, summer, fall and yes, even winter (in its own way) as well as being a lovely cut flower that dries fantastically, so now they can even be enjoyed indoors. But nothing but a camera can capture the beautiful green vibrance of this hydrangea! name: Ornamental Kale
description:
Signed Original Fine Art Photography Print by Kelly Ash.

Title: Ornamental Kale
Size: 8" x 10"

While most people think of Kale as a vegetable or as an ornamental bedding plant, these ornamental kale can grow into tall stalks with gorgeous rosettes in a variety of colors including pink, white and green.  They can look especially nice in an autumn bride's bouquet, but this photograph can look good in your living room, kitchen, hall or office!
